headline: Specialized Consumer Services Stocks Q1 Teardown: Pool (NASDAQ:POOL) Vs The Rest
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how specialized consumer services stocks fared in Q1, starting with Pool (NASDAQ:POOL).
